| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1484 — Recovery Inhibition (cactus)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8d798e6c-bfc5-5f59-a2e4-00b9814284ca"
